	(72,1,'2017-08-04 16:01:55','2017-08-04 16:01:55','<div class=\"tabs\">The Teledent Dental Placement Agency offers a variety of services for <b>Dental Offices</b> and <b>Applicants</b>. It is our goal to make the best possible matches between job applicants and Dental offices. We screen all of our applicants and assess their education, skills, and work experience, to determine whether they would be a good fit for a prospective office.</div>\r\n<div class=\"region region-content\">\r\n<div id=\"block-system-main\" class=\"block block-system\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<div id=\"node-12\" class=\"node node-page node-full node-full clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\r\n\r\nIn order to access our services, and the features of this website, you must register with Teledent by going to the <a href=\"http://teledent.ca/login\">login</a> page and signing up as a new user.\r\n\r\nWhen you log into your account, you\'ll see an option to register, and tips for getting started. Please fill out all of this information. You can come back to the site and login to update your information at any time.\r\n\r\nOur services include:\r\n\r\n• Temporary/Permanent Placements\r\n• Working Interviews\r\n• Applicant Searches\r\n• Resume Consultation\r\n• Dental Office Consultation\r\n• On-site Coaching Services\r\n• Forms and Office Manuals\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Services','','publish','closed','closed','','services','','','2017-08-04 16:01:55','2017-08-04 16:01:55','',0,'http://teledent.dev/?page_id=72',0,'page','',0),
